(1, 1, 1, 'Edelweiss Hotel', 'Edelweiss Hotel', 3, 20, 'www.edelweiss.mn', 'iHotel', 'iHotel', '976-11312186', 'info@ihotel.mn', 'Chagdarjav street-20, Ulaanbaatar Mongolia', 'Chagdarjav street-20, Ulaanbaatar Mongolia', 'Our experienced staffs are all professionally trained and speak in popular international languages of English and other foreign languages. It retains the personal feel of Mongolia whilst offering super service by hearts of friendly staffs.\r\nIt is a main landmark in the city center of Ulaanbaatar due to its convenient location close to the foreign embassies such as Czech Republic, Japan and South Korea, Chinggis Khaan Square, business and entertainment activities. \r\nWe may offer you delicious Mongolian and European cuisines, which prepared by our Master cooks. Our goal is to provide our guests with quick and friendly service. \r\nWe look forward to welcoming our guests from worldwide every day.', 'Our experienced staffs are all professionally trained and speak in popular international languages of English and other foreign languages. It retains the personal feel of Mongolia whilst offering super service by hearts of friendly staffs.\r\nIt is a main landmark in the city center of Ulaanbaatar due to its convenient location close to the foreign embassies such as Czech Republic, Japan and South Korea, Chinggis Khaan Square, business and entertainment activities. \r\nWe may offer you delicious Mongolian and European cuisines, which prepared by our Master cooks. Our goal is to provide our guests with quick and friendly service. \r\nWe look forward to welcoming our guests from worldwide every day.', 1, 1, 'img/uploads/hotels/7182e96f74449ab79d7346ecf18bc142.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:23:"img/uploads/default.jpg";}', NULL, NULL, 'Edelweiss Hotel is 3 star hotel and it has been continuously serving business travelers and tourists since 1996.', 'Edelweiss Hotel is 3 star hotel and it has been continuously serving business travelers and tourists since 1996.', NULL,