(4, 1, 1, 'Flower Hotel ', 'Flower Hotel ', 3, 64, 'www.flower-hotel.mn', 'iHotel', 'iHotel', '976-11458330', 'info@ihotel.mn', ' Zaluuchuud Avenue, 18, Bayanzurkh,Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia', ' Zaluuchuud Avenue, 18, Bayanzurkh,Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia', 'Flower Hotel has three stars and capable of hosting 330 guests in 180 standard, semi-lux and deluxe rooms. The hotel is centrally located in the middle of poplar trees on the top of a hill yet away from the traffic noise of the city while spectacular views of Bogd Khaan Mountain Range poses to the south. The hotel is located within 20 minutes car ride from the Chinggis Khaan International Airport while the central train station is within less than ten minutes driving when traffic is less busy. The city’s main land mark of Sukhbaatar square, business and shopping centres, theatres, museums and galleries are all within 20 minutes walking distance from the hotel.\r\n\r\nOur experienced staffs are all professionally trained and speak in popular international languages of English, Japanese, Chinese and Russian.  So you can feel at home in Flower Hotel while you are being served by our friendly staff. Thus we were selected one of the best customer oriented hotels in Ulaanbaatar by the Hotel Association in Mongolia.\r\n', 'Flower Hotel has three stars and capable of hosting 330 guests in 180 standard, semi-lux and deluxe rooms. The hotel is centrally located in the middle of poplar trees on the top of a hill yet away from the traffic noise of the city while spectacular views of Bogd Khaan Mountain Range poses to the south. The hotel is located within 20 minutes car ride from the Chinggis Khaan International Airport while the central train station is within less than ten minutes driving when traffic is less busy. The city’s main land mark of Sukhbaatar square, business and shopping centres, theatres, museums and galleries are all within 20 minutes walking distance from the hotel.\r\n\r\nOur experienced staffs are all professionally trained and speak in popular international languages of English, Japanese, Chinese and Russian.  So you can feel at home in Flower Hotel while you are being served by our friendly staff. Thus we were selected one of the best customer oriented hotels in Ulaanbaatar by the Hotel Association in Mongolia.\r\n', 0, 1, 'img/uploads/hotels/62f077c779bc6a4b5dce005f00d0c69f.jpg', 'a:8:{i:0;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/a0a7650cb1b69a52e2feaf83741fe0cb.jpg";i:1;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/ab7defc211d8ceaef0ab3fe7998b790f.jpg";i:2;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/97edfd3fb49f4e4c95ba03889cfd6cf9.jpg";i:3;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/22aafb47f3c8767e28014676d7ff6491.jpg";i:4;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/349aae534ec19a9e7acda26f7c8a487c.jpg";i:5;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/a63b44a49ff27533dd287eff87183edb.jpg";i:6;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/ec63bc46744b3bf37c1d15ff8df8f60a.jpg";i:7;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/a6833345e9024318c1079be04e26c7d8.jpg";}', NULL, NULL, 'Chinggis Khan Statue is 1.6 km from Flower Hotel Ulaanbaatar, while National Museum of Mongolian History is 1.7 km ', 'Chinggis Khan Statue is 1.6 km from Flower Hotel Ulaanbaatar, while National Museum of Mongolian History is 1.7 km ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '[47.924491973305,106.93817138672]', 'зоригт.анхаарах.хуруу', 'saving.masts.pile', 1, 0, 0.00, 128, 1, 7, 'DNFQck6Lkp', '2017-05-08 03:03:39', '2017-05-11 14:11:00'),
(5, 1, 1, 'UB City Hotel', 'UB City Hotel', 4, 31, NULL, 'iHotel', 'iHotel', '+976 99066350', 'info@ihotel.mn', 'Chinggis avenue, second khoroo, Ulaanbaatar city, Mongolia,', ' Chinggis avenue, second khoroo, Ulaanbaatar city, Mongolia,', 'Offering mountain views, all rooms come with a cable TV, a minibar and air conditioning. There is a kitchenette with a microwave and a refrigerator. Featuring a hairdryer, private bathrooms also come with a bathrobe and slippers.\r\n\r\nAt UB City Hotel you will find a 24-hour front desk. Other facilities offered include luggage storage. The property offers free parking.\r\n\r\nCity UB Hotel is 2.1 km from Zaisan Memorial and 2.3 km from Zanabazar Museum of Fine Arts. Chinggis Khaan International Airport is 12 km away.', 'Offering mountain views, all rooms come with a cable TV, a minibar and air conditioning. There is a kitchenette with a microwave and a refrigerator. Featuring a hairdryer, private bathrooms also come with a bathrobe and slippers.\r\n\r\nAt UB City Hotel you will find a 24-hour front desk. Other facilities offered include luggage storage. The property offers free parking.\r\n\r\nCity UB Hotel is 2.1 km from Zaisan Memorial and 2.3 km from Zanabazar Museum of Fine Arts. Chinggis Khaan International Airport is 12 km away. \r\n', 0, 1, 'img/uploads/hotels/ab4f44faf4db19943f180f45d2518f5e.jpg', 'a:7:{i:0;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/61ea0e20e534eff86d1790d92975dcd2.jpg";i:1;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/3e3016e939123763d2abcf625fc37580.jpg";i:2;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/3de8326eb7fb6ec2925c9f00bfdf303e.jpg";i:3;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/fc354ec89af724ea5faa475e90154eb5.jpg";i:4;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/448214ecf153abd574ab3698acb88e07.jpg";i:5;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/37914b41e204adbf489ca6ef83fd71f2.jpg";i:6;s:55:"img/uploads/hotels/cf66e61db574d2b776ac6da08c36f35a.jpg";}', NULL, NULL, 'UB City Hotel is located in Ulaanbaatar, a 4-minute drive National Stadium', 'UB City Hotel is located in Ulaanbaatar, a 4-minute drive Nationa